DAPAR2 0.6

Similar to the function is.na but focused on the equality with the paramter 'type'.

is.OfType.Rd

Similar to the function is.na but focused on the equality with the paramter 'type'.

is.OfType(data, type)

Arguments

data

A data.frame
type

The value to search in the dataframe

Value

A boolean dataframe

Author

Samuel Wieczorek

Examples

library(QFeatures)
utils::data(Exp1_R25_pept, package='DAPARdata2')
obj <- Exp1_R25_pept
data <- rowData(Exp1_R25_pept[['original']])[,metadata(Exp1_R25_pept)$OriginOfValues]
is.OfType(as.data.frame(data@listData), "MEC")
